##  How to Use

1. **Install Stylus**: Download and install the **Stylus** extension from the [Chrome Web Store](https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/stylus/clngdbigpbobmmoedihgandbffonhgha).
2. **Get the Code**: Copy the entire CSS code from `gemini-theme.user.css` in this repository.
3. **Create New Style**:
   * Open [Gemini](https://gemini.google.com/).
   * Click the **Stylus** extension icon in your browser toolbar.
   * Click on **"Write style for: gemini.google.com"** (click the URL text).
4. **Paste and Save**: Paste the copied code into the Stylus editor text area, give it a name on the left sidebar, and press `Ctrl + S` (or `Cmd + S` on Mac) to save.
5. **Done**: Go back to Gemini, and the minimalist UI will be applied automatically!
